      "task_title": "Parikshak Deterministic Task Evaluation with FastAPI Rule Engine and Governance",
      "task_description": "Implement a full-stack deterministic engineering task evaluation system using FastAPI as the backend framework with modular service architecture. The system must include a rule engine that evaluates submissions as PASS or FAIL based on strict binary checks for schema validation, completeness, logic alignment, and integration integrity. Build a signal engine to collect supporting signals from repositories and task descriptions, including feature matching and delivery ratio computation. Implement a task graph engine for deterministic task selection after each evaluation. Add a governance layer with an immutable event journal, SQLite canonical database, and complete audit trail. Create a React frontend for task submission and a review dashboard. Include observability hooks, API route modules, and comprehensive test coverage using pytest.",
